<h1>Takeaway Finder</h1>

<p>Takeaway Finder is a web application that helps users find nearby takeaway restaurants using Google Maps integration and the Just Eat Takeaway API.</p>

<h2>How to Use</h2>

<ol>
    <li>Navigate to the <strong>Find Takeaway</strong> page.</li>
    <li>Enter a valid UK postcode in the search field.</li>
    <li>Press <strong>Search</strong> to find nearby restaurants.</li>
    <li>View the results displayed as markers on the map.</li>
</ol>

<p>
    To get the project running locally, follow the setup instructions in the
    <a href="https://github.com/zain-ahmed0/TakeawayFinder" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">README</a>.
</p>